  "stem": "<p style=\"text-align: left;\">A line intersects two parallel lines, forming four acute angles and four obtuse angles. The measure of one of these eight angles is <math alttext=\"left parenthesis 7 x minus 250 right parenthesis degree\"><mfenced><mrow><mn>7</mn><mi>x</mi><mo>-</mo><mn>250</mn></mrow></mfenced><mo>&#176;</mo></math>. The sum of the measures of four of the eight angles is <math alttext=\"k degree\"><mi>k</mi><mo>&#176;</mo></math>. Which of the following could NOT be equivalent to <math alttext=\"k\"><mi>k</mi>\n</math>, for all values of <math alttext=\"x\"><mi>x</mi>\n</math>?</p>",
